cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper focuses on developing a convolutional neural network approach for gait recognition based on silhouette sequence images, which falls under the domain of computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed network is trained in an end-to-end manner, indicating the use of machine learning techniques. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper involves the development of a neural network-based approach for gait recognition, which can be considered as an application of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the processing and analysis of gait silhouette sequence images, which can be considered as a multimedia data type. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper involves the development of a neural network-based approach for gait recognition, which falls under the domain of neural computing.
